	<ThingDef Name="YaomaXenotype_XuanwuArmorBase" ParentName="ArmorMachineableBase">
		<defName>YaomaXenotype_Tier1_Xuanwu</defName>
		<label>xuanwu armor</label>
		<description>A lamellar armor that’s been a reliable constant in early Yaoma history. Equipped by warriors on the front lines, its enjoined plates provide noticeable protection without compromising movement severely. With good defense against slashing and blunt attacks, the Yaoma fielded xuanwu armor for generations to come.</description>
